My ads get rejected for being clickbait while they are not.

I'm sorry to hear that your ads are being rejected for being clickbait. Ad rejection reasons can vary, and it's important to understand the specific reason provided by Ad Support. I recommend checking the email you received from Ad Support for details on why your ad was rejected. Additionally, you can review our advertising policy to ensure your ad complies with all guidelines. Here is a helpful article on what to do next after an ad gets rejected: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next). If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!
